Class PortableDataStreamDataSetIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.spark.iterator.PortableDataStreamDataSetIterator

  • public class PortableDataStreamDataSetIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    A DataSetIterator that loads serialized DataSet objects (saved with DataSet#save(OutputStream)) from a PortableDataStream, usually obtained from SparkContext.binaryFiles()
